=================== CI ========================
- developer push code ke github -> Job Jenkins CI otomatis trigger
- build & Test maven (Java)
- Sonarqube buat quality scan, ada webhook yang bakal mengirim jawaban (passed/failed) ke jenkins
- kalo passed build & push image ke dockerhub
- Jenkins CI kirim IMAGE_TAG ke Jenkins CD (stage Trigger CD Pipeline)

===================== CD =========================
- job jalan karena dapet trigger dari Jenkins CI
- pull repo gitops
- update file deployment.yaml dengan image tag terbaru 
- push code terbaru ke repo gitops

======================= ArgoCD ===================
- ketika repo gitops commit akan terdetect di argocd (commit file deployment.yml terbaru)
- pull manifest terbaru dari gitops repo
- EKS pull image dari Docker Hub sesuai tag di deployment.yaml
- apply ke EKS cluster buat update pod dengan image baru dari dockerhub (ini connect repo, cluster dulu)